    think='We have successfully completed all tasks. Let me provide a final summ
ary to the user.\n\nKey actions taken:\n1. Fixed SQL named parameters to positio
nal `?` placeholders with correct parameter array (23 entries).\n2. Added JWT au
thentication to MatchingGateway, extracting userId from token payload and discon
necting unauthorized clients.\n3. Injected Redis via NestJS IoC using `REDIS_CLI
ENT` provider in MatchingModule, and added `onModuleDestroy` to quit connection.
\n4. Unified age calculation by selecting `birth_date` in SQL and using `calcula
teAge()` in both DB and cache hit paths.\n5. Added clearing of target user\'s re
commendation cache in `recordSwipeAction`.\n6. Added `ProfileCompletionGuard` to
`GET /matches`.\n7. Tightened CORS to `process.env.CLIENT_URL || "https://app.so
cialworld.com"`.\n8. Validated `limit` parameter (1-100, default 20).\n9. Used d
river error code `ER_DUP_ENTRY` / `errno === 1062` for duplicate key detection w
ith fallback.\n10. Added `_isFetchingMore` lock in `MatchListCubit` to prevent d
uplicate pagination requests.\n11. Removed `super_like` from docs.\n12. Fixed UR
L regex in `matching_socket_client.dart` to handle optional trailing slash.\n13.
Updated mobile socket client to pass token via `auth` instead of `userId` via `q
uery`.\n14. Fixed BDD test setup to provide `REDIS_CLIENT` mock.\n\nAll tests pa
ssed:\n- API unit tests: 49 passed\n- BDD tests: 69 passed\n- Mobile tests: 32 p
assed\n- Design-system tests: 8 passed\n- Builds: API, Admin, Shared-types, Mobi
le APK all built successfully.\n- Pre-commit and pre-push hooks passed.\n- Pushe
d 2 commits to `feat/issue-43`.\n\nOne minor note: the `adb` command is not foun
d in the environment, which causes a non-fatal warning in the pre-push hook but 
